{"type":"message","id":"cfffead2","parentId":"df656fad","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:27:40.860Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5g6ulix4c7yg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 142713\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: a (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine what ONE concrete action to take.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\r\n- Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n- A CFI Compression Experiment was completed showing CFI ≥ 0.7 AND freq < 60 is too aggressive\r\n- The next pending action is: \"Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\"\r\n\r\nThe pending action clearly states:\r\n- Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n- Test: does this distinguish \"constant format\" (freq≈160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)?\r\n- Run: 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n\r\nThis is the most concrete next step. I should implement and run this experiment.\r\n\r\nLet me look at what's available:\r\n1. I need to find the previous experiment data/results to build upon\r\n2. I need to run the hybrid scoring experiment\r\n\r\nThe recent pulse is `pulse_2026-03-24 142615.md` - this was the last pulse.\r\n\r\nLooking at the CFI Compression Synthesis doc mentioned: `research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md`\r\n\r\nThe action should be:\r\n- Implement the hybrid scoring formula in the experiment\r\n- Run the comparison with binary thresholds\r\n\r\nLet me check what experiment files exist and create/modify the experiment script.\r\n\r\nActually, I should be more specific. The experiment requires:\r\n1. Data from previous runs (200 pulses worth)\r\n2. The scoring formula implementation\r\n3. Comparison against binary thresholds\r\n\r\nI need to either:\r\n- Modify an existing experiment script\r\n- Create a new experiment script\r\n\r\nLet me look for existing experiment scripts in the sandbox. Common locations would be:\r\n- `research/`\r\n- `experiments/`\r\n\r\n\r\n- Or as part of `pulse.ps1`\r\n\r\nI'll prioritize creating an experiment script that tests the hybrid scoring formula directly. The key steps involve calculating the new score and comparing it against the existing binary threshold method. I'll focus on implementing the formula: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120).\r\n\r\nMy next action is to draft the experiment script that will validate this approach, ensuring I can differentiate between constant format and research trajectory data points.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe next experiment is clearly defined: test the hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5 scoring formula against binary thresholds. The formula `score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)` should distinguish constant-format tokens (freq≈160, CFI=1) from research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5).\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the experiment script implementing the hybrid scoring formula and run the comparison against binary thresholds on 200 pulses (80/20 split).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Experiment (Strategy C)\r\n# Date: 2026-03-24\r\n# Goal: Test if CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) distinguishes constant-format from research trajectory\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$PulseCount = 200,\r\n    [double]$TrainSplit = 0.8\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$ProjectRoot = Split-Path (Split-Path $PSScriptRoot -Parent) -Parent\r\n\r\n# Load pulse history\r\n$pulseHistoryPath = Join-Path $ProjectRoot \"research/pulse_history.json\"\r\nif (-not (Test-Path $pulseHistoryPath)) {\r\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] Pulse history not found: $pulseHistoryPath\"\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n$pulses = Get-Content $pulseHistoryPath | ConvertFrom-Json\r\nWrite-Host \"[INFO] Loaded $($pulses.Count) pulses\"\r\n\r\n# Calculate metrics for each token\r\nfunction Get-TokenMetrics {\r\n    param([string]$Token, [array]$PulseTokens)\r\n    \r\n    $total = $PulseTokens.Count\r\n    $freq = ($PulseTokens | Where-Object { $_ -eq $Token }).Count\r\n    $cfi = if ($total -gt 0) { $freq / $total } else { 0 }\r\n    \r\n    return @{\r\n        Token = $Token\r\n        Freq = $freq\r\n        CFI = $cfi\r\n        HybridScore = $cfi * [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Compute metrics across all pulses\r\n$tokenPool = @{}\r\nforeach ($pulse in $pulses) {\r\n    foreach ($token in $pulse.tokens) {\r\n        if (-not $tokenPool.ContainsKey($token)) {\r\n            $tokenPool[$token] = 0\r\n        }\r\n        $tokenPool[$token]++\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Calculate hybrid scores\r\n$tokenMetrics = $tokenPool.Keys | ForEach-Object {\r\n    Get-TokenMetrics -Token $_ -PulseTokens @()\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Recalculate with correct frequency\r\n$allTokens = @()\r\nforeach ($pulse in $pulses) {\r\n    $allTokens += $pulse.tokens\r\n}\r\n\r\n$uniqueTokens = $tokenPool.Keys | ForEach-Object {\r\n    $t = $_\r\n    $freq = $tokenPool[$t]\r\n    $cfi = $freq / $pulses.Count\r\n    $hybridScore = $cfi * [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    \r\n    [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        Token = $t\r\n        Freq = $freq\r\n        CFI = [Math]::Round($cfi, 4)\r\n        HybridScore = [Math]::Round($hybridScore, 4)\r\n        IsResearch = ($\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:27:33\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774376860858}}
